      "FlowOrchestrator(new): orchestrate 'place_order' steps and trigger rollback on failures",
      "FlowTraceService(new): propagate traceId/spanId across logs/metrics",
      "CompensationService(new): a set of re-entrant compensations",
      "OutboxEventService(new): persist events and dispatch asynchronously",
